<paragraph id="BE75699B67EBEB3056ADAA347EEF675D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BOLIVIA. 
<emphasis id="EFE3BF3C525C70267958B92A9B4DF562" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">M. Bang</emphasis>
2506 (lectotype NY00319206, designated here; isolectotype US).
